'''河马汗酸'''是一种在[[河马|河马]]的[[皮膚|皮膚]]分泌物中发现的红[[色素|色素]]<ref>{{cite journal | journal = Pure Appl. Chem. | volume = 79 | issue = 4 | pages = 507–517 | year = 2007 | doi = 10.1351/pac200779040507 | title = Studies on the red sweat of the Hippopotamus amphibius | author = Kimiko Hashimoto, Yoko Saikawa, and Masaya Nakata | url = http://media.iupac.org/publications/pac/2007/pdf/7904x0507.pdf | access-date = 2015-01-10 | archive-date = 2014-08-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140809133032/http://media.iupac.org/publications/pac/2007/pdf/7904x0507.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>。虽然这种分泌物通常被称为“血汗”（因而命名为“hipposudoric”，指的是“河马（hippo）汗（sweat）”），然而它既不是血，也不是汗。

像它的橙色[[结构类似物|类似物]]去甲河马汗酸，河马汗酸既可作为天然[[防曬油|防曬油]]，也可作为[[抗微生物|抗菌]]剂。它可由[[尿黑酸|尿黑酸]]氧化二聚而得。<ref>{{cite journal | title = Properties of the enzyme responsible to the synthesis of hipposudoric and norhipposudoric acids, the pigments in the red sweat of the hippopotamus | author = Moriya Kai, Matsuura Masanori, Saikawa Yoko, Hashimoto Kimiko, Yamaguguchi Ayumu, Sakamoto Kazuhiro, Akihisa Narito, Hirata Hiroyoshi | journal = Nippon Kagakkai Koen Yokoshu | volume = 86 | issue = 2 | pages = 1314 | year = 2006 | url = http://sciencelinks.jp/j-east/article/200618/000020061806A0436283.php | access-date = 2015-01-10 | archive-date = 2012-02-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120217004657/http://sciencelinks.jp/j-east/article/200618/000020061806A0436283.php | dead-url = no }}</ref>

